---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - KPPF.EU" description="Learn about KPPF - premium paint protection film manufacturer serving the European market from Sweden.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About <span class="text-amber-400">KPPF</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Crafted by professionals, for professionals. We deliver premium paint protection film to detailing studios across Europe.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-amber-400">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">KPPF was born from a simple idea: detailing professionals deserve materials that match their skill level. Too many films on the market compromise on quality, forcing masters to work around material limitations instead of focusing on results.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We partnered with leading polyurethane film manufacturers to develop a product line that meets the highest standards — self-healing without heat, chemical resistance, anti-yellowing technology, and a deep gloss finish that enhances every vehicle's appearance.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Now, we're bringing this same commitment to quality to the European market, with our headquarters in Stockholm, Sweden.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-800 rounded-2xl h-80 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">Company Photo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-amber-400">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-gray-700 hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏆</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Every roll of KPPF film undergoes rigorous quality control. We never compromise on materials or manufacturing standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-gray-700 hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Professional Partnership</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">We work directly with detailing studios, providing training, support, and materials that help them deliver exceptional results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-gray-700 hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">European Commitment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Local presence, fast delivery, and dedicated European support. We're here to serve the growing PPF market across Europe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why KPPF -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-amber-400">Why Choose KPPF?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="text-amber-400 text-2xl flex-shrink-0">✓</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Self-Healing Technology</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Minor scratches disappear naturally without heat treatment — just sunlight or warm water.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="text-amber-400 text-2xl flex-shrink-0">✓</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Up to 7 Years Durability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Long-lasting protection that maintains clarity and performance year after year.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="text-amber-400 text-2xl flex-shrink-0">✓</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Anti-Yellowing Formula</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Advanced UV-resistant coating prevents yellowing, keeping your vehicle looking fresh.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="text-amber-400 text-2xl flex-shrink-0">✓</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Easy Installation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Highly elastic film that forgives positioning errors and stretches to conform to any body shape.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-700">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Partner with KPPF?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 opacity-90">Get in touch to discuss pricing, distribution, or place your first order.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
